不过是依附于一个更为精妙故事的段子，差点沦为滑稽的模仿”，<ref name="Alexander"><cite class="citation" id="CITEREFAlexander2005">Alexander, Caroline (2005-12-11), "Myths Made Modern", ''New York Times Book Review'', p. 16</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AThe+Penelopiad&rft.atitle=Myths+Made+Modern&rft.aufirst=Caroline&rft.aulast=Alexander&rft.date=2005-12-11&rft.genre=article&rft.jtitle=New+York+Times+Book+Review&rft.pages=16&rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal"> </span>.</ref> 称它“对于女权主义叙述而言还不够口语化”，<ref name="Heller"><cite class="citation" id="CITEREFHeller2006">Heller, Amanda (2006-01-01), [http://www.boston.com/ae/books/articles/2006/01/01/short_takes_boston_globe/ "Short Takes"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.boston.com/ae/books/articles/2006/01/01/short_takes_boston_globe/ |date=20160303193725 }}, ''The Boston Globe''<span class="reference-accessdate">, retrieved <span class="nowrap">2008-02-28</span></span></cite><cite class="citation" id="CITEREFHeller2006"></cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AThe+Penelopiad&rft.atitle=Short+Takes&rft.aufirst=Amanda&rft.aulast=Heller&rft.date=2006-01-01&rft.genre=article&rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.boston.com%2Fae%2Fbooks%2Farticles%2F2006%2F01%2F01%2Fshort_takes_boston_globe%2F&rft.jtitle=The+Boston+Globe&rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal"> </span>.</ref> 并指出，唱诗女仆一段尤为糟粕，对她们的形象塑造流于表面，不够入木三分。<ref name="Alexander"><cite class="citation" id="CITEREFAlexander2005">Alexander, Caroline (2005-12-11), "Myths Made Modern", ''New York Times Book Review'', p. 16</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AThe+Penelopiad&rft.atitle=Myths+Made+Modern&rft.aufirst=Caroline&rft.aulast=Alexander&rft.date=2005-12-11&rft.genre=article&rft.jtitle=New+York+Times+Book+Review&rft.pages=16&rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal"> </span>.</ref> 伊丽莎白·汉德在[[华盛顿邮报|华盛顿邮报]]上写道该书“较[[蒙提·派森|蒙提·派森]]的笔法远为逊色”。<ref name="Hand"><cite class="citation" id="CITEREFHand2005">Hand, Elizabeth (2005-12-25), [http://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/article/2005/12/22/AR2005122201568.html "The New Muses"], ''[[华盛顿邮报|The Washington Post]]'', p. </cite></ref>在《英语研究》杂志中，奥丁·德克和L. R. 利维斯形容这本书是“刻意的自我放纵”，读起来像“[[威廉·S·吉尔伯特|威廉·S·吉尔伯特]]过了头”，好比温迪·可普把[[T·S·艾略特|T·S·艾略特]]的[[荒原_(詩)|荒原]]写成了远不及原作的五行打油诗。<ref><cite class="citation" id="CITEREFDekkersLeavis2007">Dekkers, Odin; Leavis, L. R. (December 2007), "Current Literature 2005. </cite></ref>

== 戏剧化改编 ==
爱特伍在2005年10月26日[[菲利达·劳埃德|菲利达·劳埃德]]在[[皮卡迪利圣雅各教堂|皮卡迪利圣詹姆斯教堂]]举办的一次戏剧阅读会之后完成了该书剧本的草稿。<ref name="Taylor">{{citation | first = Craig | last = Taylor | url = http://www.walrusmagazine.com/articles/2007.10--margaret-atwood-novel/ | title = Twelve Angry Maids | newspaper = [[The_Walrus|The Walrus]] | date = October 2007 | access-date = 2008-03-07 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20080704131751/http://www.walrusmagazine.com/articles/2007.10--margaret-atwood-novel/ | archive-date = 2008-07-04 | url-status = dead }}.</ref> [[加拿大国家艺术中心|加拿大国家艺术中心]]和英国[[皇家莎士比亞劇團|皇家莎士比亚剧团]]对该剧本都表达了合作的意愿。排演该剧的经费主要从九位加拿大女士处筹集，她们每人都向艺术中心捐赠了50,000[[加拿大元|加拿大元]]，人们戏称他们为“佩涅罗珀集团”。<ref>{{citation | first = Mitch | last = Potter | url = https://www.thestar.com/comment/columnists/article/242766 | title = Stage version of Atwood novel gets warm embrace | newspaper = [[多倫多星報|The Toronto Star]] | date = 2007-08-03 | place = Stratford-Upon-Avon | access-date = 2008-03-07 | archive-date = 2012-03-20 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20120320082518/http://www.thestar.com/comment/columnists/article/242766 }}.</ref><ref>{{citation|year=2007 |title=The Penelope Circle |place=Ottawa |publisher=National Arts Centre Foundation |url=http://www.nac-cna.ca/en/theatre/the_penelopiad/circle.asp |archive-url=https://wayback.archive-it.org/all/20080302090818/http://www.nac-cna.ca/en/theatre/the_penelopiad/circle.asp |url-status=dead |archive-date=2008-03-02 |access-date=2008-03-07 }}</ref>演职人员均为女性，由七名加拿大演员和六名英国演员组成，由乔塞特·明戈-布谢尔担任导演，维罗妮卡·坦南特担任编舞。<ref name="Morrow"/>由打击乐器、键盘乐器和大提琴组成的音乐三重奏均布置在舞台上。全体人员于2007年6月到7月在[[埃文河畔斯特拉特福|埃文河畔斯特拉特福]]排演。<ref>{{citation | first = Catherine | last = Lawson | title = Penelope speaks; Atwood's monologues a joy, says British actress | newspaper = Ottawa Citizen | date = 2007-09-19 |page=E1}}.</ref>这部100分钟的舞台剧将于7月27日到8月18日在位于渥太华的国家艺术中心与观众见面。爱特伍的剧本并未对舞台有太多限定，这给了导演明戈-布谢尔一定发挥的空间。两国评论家都对由彭尼·唐尼扮演的佩涅罗珀充满赞誉，但他们觉得这部戏剧叙述太多而编剧不足。<ref name="Marlowe">{{citation | first = Sam | last = Marlowe | url = http://entertainment.timesonline.co.uk/tol/arts_and_entertainment/specials/edinburgh/article2196598.ece | title = The Penelopiad | newspaper = [[泰晤士报|The Times]] | date = 2007-08-06 | access-date = 2008-03-07 | archive-date = 2011-06-16 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110616040906/http://entertainment.timesonline.co.uk/tol/arts_and_entertainment/specials/edinburgh/article2196598.ece }}.</ref><ref>{{citation | date = 2007-09-22 | title = An epic tragedy with a whole lot of sparkle | newspaper = [[多倫多星報|Toronto Star]] |page=A23}}.</ref> 在排演过程中两国艺术家做过一些调整，使得原本明戈-布谢尔导演中唱诗女仆情感匮乏的缺点通过加拿大演员的表演得到弥补。<ref>{{citation | first = Kamal | last = Al-Solaylee | url = https://www.theglobeandmail.com/servlet/story/RTGAM.20070804.wpenelope0804/BNStory/Entertainment/Theatre/ | title = Atwood's baby has come a long way | newspaper = [[The_Globe_and_Mail|The Globe and Mail]] | date = 2007-08-04 | page = R1 | access-date = 2008-03-07 | url-status = dead | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20080313234433/http://www.theglobeandmail.com/servlet/story/RTGAM.20070804.wpenelope0804/BNStory/Entertainment/Theatre/ | archive-date = 2008-03-13 }}.</ref><ref>{{citation | first = Kamal | last = Al-Solaylee | title = A hit, but not a home run | newspaper = [[The_Globe_and_Mail|The Globe and Mail]] | date = 2007-09-24 |page=R1}}.</ref> 随后，该剧还于2011年10月26日和11月20日在位于温哥华的斯坦利产业联盟剧场进行汇演。<ref>{{citation | first = Colin | last = Thomas | url = https://www.straight.com/article-516466/vancouver/penelopiad-container-some-interesting-politics | title = The Penelopiad is a container for some interesting politics | newspaper = [[The_Georgia_Straight|The Georgia Straight]] | date = 2011-10-27 | access-date = 2011-11-03 | url-status = dead | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20111102061327/http://www.straight.com/article-516466/vancouver/penelopiad-container-some-interesting-politics | archive-date = 2011-11-02 }}.</ref> 在多伦多，该剧于2012年1月10-29日在夜林剧场和坏时代的伙伴剧院演出。<ref>{{citation | url = http://www.nightwoodtheatre.net/index.php/whats_on/the_penelopiad | title = The Penelopiad | publisher = [[Nightwood_Theatre|Nightwood Theatre]] | year = 2011 | access-date = 2011-11-03 | archive-date = 2012-01-18 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20120118073648/http://www.nightwoodtheatre.net/index.php/whats_on/the_penelopiad }}.</ref>夜林剧院的演出由凯利·松顿导演，由莫妮卡担任编舞，[[梅根·法蘿|梅根·法萝]]主演。[[环球邮报|《环球邮报》]]给该剧的评分为3.5分（满分4分）。<ref>{{citation | first = J. Kelly | last = Nestruck | title = Fine female cast makes for a magical Penelopiad | newspaper = [[The_Globe_and_Mail|The Globe and Mail]] | date = 2012-01-13 | url = https://www.theglobeandmail.com/news/arts/theatre/fine-female-cast-makes-for-a-magical-penelopiad/article2301641/ | access-date = January 13, 2012 | archive-date = 2012-01-14 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20120114094757/https://www.theglobeandmail.com/news/arts/theatre/fine-female-cast-makes-for-a-magical-penelopiad/article2301641/ }}.</ref>

